  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don’t Drop the Soap</strong> is a darkly humorous 2D platformer set in a brutal prison where you control a bar of soap trying not to fall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c108ddd2d2488a76273d25ae60324890.poster.avif?t=1748028103\" width=800 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c108ddd2d2488a76273d25ae60324890.webm?t=1748028103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c108ddd2d2488a76273d25ae60324890.mp4?t=1748028103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by retro rage games and classic side-scrollers, this game offers:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧼 25 unique, hand-designed prison-themed levels<br>💀 Deadly traps, rolling enemies, and ghost guards<br>🕹️ Fast-paced, relentless gameplay with precise controls<br>🏆 Unlockable achievements for getting shot, scared, crushed, and flushed<br>🎵 Original soundtrack (also available as DLC)<br>💸 Priced under <strong>$1.00</strong> — perfect for fans of cheap, fun, and challenging games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you like meme games, punishing platformers, or just want to laugh while repeatedly dying, <i>Don’t Drop the Soap</i> delivers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c6e4a1bf9a2686be0976e687dfeb5457.avif?t=1748028103\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras_big/c6e4a1bf9a2686be0976e687dfeb5457.avif?t=1748028103 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don’t Drop the Soap</strong> is a darkly humorous 2D platformer set in a brutal prison where you control a bar of soap trying not to fall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c108ddd2d2488a76273d25ae60324890.poster.avif?t=1748028103\" width=800 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c108ddd2d2488a76273d25ae60324890.webm?t=1748028103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c108ddd2d2488a76273d25ae60324890.mp4?t=1748028103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by retro rage games and classic side-scrollers, this game offers:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧼 25 unique, hand-designed prison-themed levels<br>💀 Deadly traps, rolling enemies, and ghost guards<br>🕹️ Fast-paced, relentless gameplay with precise controls<br>🏆 Unlockable achievements for getting shot, scared, crushed, and flushed<br>🎵 Original soundtrack (also available as DLC)<br>💸 Priced under <strong>$1.00</strong> — perfect for fans of cheap, fun, and challenging games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you like meme games, punishing platformers, or just want to laugh while repeatedly dying, <i>Don’t Drop the Soap</i> delivers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras/c6e4a1bf9a2686be0976e687dfeb5457.avif?t=1748028103\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652910/extras_big/c6e4a1bf9a2686be0976e687dfeb5457.avif?t=1748028103 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
